<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Albert Park/Radisson Heights</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The Albert Park/Radisson Heights Real estate offers some of the most spectacular views of the enigmatic Bow River Valley and the majestic Canadian Rockies. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">With a long and glorious history of more than a century, the Albert Park/Radisson Heights is a spectacular residential community located within the south-east quadrant of Calgary. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Its ample open spaces and central location with respect to all major public amenities and recreational venues renders Albert Park/Radisson Heights one of the most desirable communities in SE Calgary.</p>
        </div>
